description:
The plan is in full swing however - Big Mom is pushed past the edge of sanity and can`t even bring herself to act. Meanwhile, her children make a move against Germa and Pudding takes up her original aim of killing Sanji!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Die Mission ist fehlgeschlagen? – Der Gegenangriff der Big Mom-Piraten!
L`échec du plan ! L`équipage de Big Mom contre-attque
Sakusen Shippai!? Hangeki no Big Mom Kaizokudan
The Mission Failed?! The Big Mom Pirates Strike Back!
План провален! Пираты Большой Мамочки наносят ответный удар!
作戦失敗!? 反撃のビッグ・マム海賊団
